They were of similar status.

454
00:40:53,370 --> 00:40:55,300
Tell me.

455
00:40:55,840 --> 00:40:58,550
Who do you want to start with?

456
00:40:59,940 --> 00:41:03,840
The Cabinet is full of high-ranking and powerful ministers.

457
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:08,210
Even the slightest mistake would alert them.

458
00:41:08,210 --> 00:41:10,040
Moreover, it won't be easy

459
00:41:10,040 --> 00:41:14,020
to remain an official once you offend someone.

460
00:41:15,070 --> 00:41:19,750
Naturally, I want to start with the highest-ranking minister.

461
00:41:19,750 --> 00:41:23,090
Shi Yiping, the Chief Cabinet Secretary.

462
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:36,720
Shi Yiping has always been...

463
00:41:37,330 --> 00:41:40,070
domineering and arrogant

464
00:41:40,070 --> 00:41:44,330
in the Cabinet and the Ministry of Personnel.

465
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:49,060
But after Cao Jingxian died,

466
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:52,250
rather than expanding his power,

467
00:41:52,250 --> 00:41:55,150
Mr. Shi claimed illness

468
00:41:55,150 --> 00:41:58,720
and stayed at home as if he had no more political ambitions.

469
00:42:03,420 --> 00:42:06,320
If the third enemy had obtained the Gui Seal,

470
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:08,950
he would no longer care about the officialdom.

471
00:42:09,550 --> 00:42:13,810
Sir, it seems that you know Mr. Shi quite well.

472
00:42:22,230 --> 00:42:27,050
That's why I came to see you.

